tu makes markets by providing passive quotations to buyers and sellers in more than  securities and other financial instruments on august   virtu financial along with londonbased gsa capital executed the first trades on parfx prime a foreign exchange trading platform unlike most exchanges and trading venues parfxs matching engine does not adhere to the principle of pricetime priority instead parfx subjects all orders to random pauses of about  to  milliseconds trying to provide a more level playing field when filing for its ipo in march  it was disclosed that during five years virtu financial made profit  out of  days losing money just one day gregory laughlin astrophysicist and department chairman at the university of california santa cruz researched virtus trading activity in the debate about its nearperfect trading record virtu said that it wins  percent or  percent of its trades leading most people to figure the remainder are losses in his research laughlin showed that the number of its trades that break even are about the same as its losses which means the hft firms pertrade losing percentage is only  instead of  indicating virtu assumes little market risk investigationsedit in april  new york attorney general eric schneiderman sent virtu a letter seeking information on its hft practices asking about special arrangements with dark pools and exchanges the companys trading strategies and whether virtu practices latency arbitrage a highfrequency activity considered to be front running in july  reuters reported the securities and exchange commission sec was seeking information on ten hft firms with brokerdealer licenses including virtu financial as part of an ongoing investigation into predatory trading strategies the secs probe focuses on abuse of order types and abusive trading like layering or spoofing a tactic intended to trick investors into buying or selling a stock at unfavorable prices john mccrank of reuters noted that scrutiny around highfrequency trading intensified after the release of michael lewis bestselling book flash boys a wall street revolt in march  referencesedit  a b c underhill justine april   virtu’s ipo first highfrequency trading firm to go public yahoo finance   a b c de la merced michael j april   virtu a highfrequency trader resumes its ipo new york times   a b c d e httpswwwsecgovarchivesedgardatavirtxkhtm  company overview of virtu financial inc investingbusinessweekcom business week retrieved  july    how to make a billion dollars from big data published by forbes march   retrieved  february   a b c virtu financial inc s wwwsecgov sec   a b alden william april   virtu financial said to shelve ipo plans dealbook published by the new york times retrieved october     a b httpirvirtucomreleasedetailcfmreleaseid  man vs machine seven major players in highfrequency trading cnbc september    mccrank john  june  virtu ceo urges strict standards for electronic firms that are market makers reuters retrieved  july    httpwwwsecgovcommentspdf  europe’s top  highfrequency kingmakers dow jones financial news october    mccrank john november   bats appoints chris concannon as its new president reuters retrieved november     a b virtu financial acquires amsterdam etf market maker nyenburgh holding bv pr newswire  september  retrieved  july    virtu financial llc press release ida ireland virtu financial  september  retrieved  july    two large us proprietary trading firms to merge financial times may    alliance healthcare virtu financial offer new deals wall street journal june    silver lake backs virtumadison tyler merger mergers and acquisitions june    mehta nina  december  highfrequency firm virtu buys cohen capital’s amex unit business week retrieved  july    httpirvirtucomfilesdocnewsaprvirtufinancialagreestoacquirekcgholdingssolopdf  hope bradley demos telis march   virtu ipo poised to make a multi billionaire of vinnie viola moneybeat published by the wall street journal retrieved november     virtu 