n more than  unique exchanges markets and liquidity pools around the world the group generates revenue by buying and selling large volumes of securities and other financial instruments and earning small bidask spreads in addition it also earns revenues from interest and dividend income as well as through the sale of licensed technology and related services read more read less recently viewed tickers recent activity free daily trade recommendations  virt  tts  qts  gme  fico sheldon mcintyre  oct    am  year ago  campus martius suite detroit mi      popular pages browse products become a maven become an affiliate about us get help terms of service privacy policy sec disclosure contact us send us feedback connect with us facebook twitter linkedin blog store become an affiliate become a maven contact us about terms of service privacy policy sec disclosure built by   marketfy virtu financial skip to content market making client market making customized liquidity trading solutions algorithmic trading institutional trading etf trading trading venues virtu bondpoint virtu matchit careers our culture open positions internships about us history transparency media virtu investors contact trading  technology market making expertise meets advanced technology  virtu is a leading financial firm that leverages cutting edge technology to deliver liquidity to the global markets and innovative transparent trading solutions to our clients      virtu  kcg a message to our valued clients learn more  trust  transparency learn more about virtu and our values about us  copyright   virtu financial all rights reserved virtuinvestors operating business subsidiaries global disclosures  regulatory reporting business continuity plan modern slavery statement virtu financial skip to content market making client market making customized liquidity trading solutions algorithmic trading institutional trading etf trading trading venues virtu bondpoint virtu matchit careers our culture open positions in